		\textbf{Capability}                               & \textbf{CRANE} & \textbf{Elicit} & \textbf{ResearchRabbit} & \textbf{Semantic Scholar} & \textbf{Zotero/Mendeley} \\
		\midrule
		Multi-source ingestion orchestration              & \checkmark     & No              & No                      & No                        & No                       \\
		MCP-native tool interface                         & \checkmark     & No              & No                      & No                        & No                       \\
